1
00:00:21,070 --> 00:00:24,180
♪The breeze of the 1990s drifts by♪

2
00:00:24,350 --> 00:00:27,180
♪Memories slowly flicker past♪

3
00:00:27,650 --> 00:00:31,430
♪My heartbeat
rises and falls with the tune♪

4
00:00:31,500 --> 00:00:34,580
♪The story quietly begins here♪

5
00:00:35,330 --> 00:00:38,640
♪Under the dim lights, our eyes meet♪

6
00:00:38,710 --> 00:00:41,850
♪Time seems to stand still♪

7
00:00:42,350 --> 00:00:45,990
♪Your smile
breaks through the clouds like sun♪

8
00:00:46,060 --> 00:00:49,150
♪Melting the snow deep in my heart♪

9
00:00:49,580 --> 00:00:53,090
♪Street posters spread signals of love♪

10
00:00:53,150 --> 00:00:56,110
♪Our story slowly begins to ferment♪

11
00:00:56,800 --> 00:01:00,730
♪Hand in hand,
going through every dusk corner♪

12
00:01:00,930 --> 00:01:04,800
♪The taste of happiness is so subtle♪

13
00:01:05,480 --> 00:01:08,740
♪Crossing back to the 1990s stage♪

14
00:01:09,150 --> 00:01:12,480
♪You're my most beautiful surprise♪

15
00:01:12,790 --> 00:01:16,210
♪Love's flame burns within my heart♪

16
00:01:16,680 --> 00:01:19,710
♪Not afraid of obstacles ahead♪

17
00:01:20,180 --> 00:01:23,560
♪Sway with the rhythm.
Feel your heart pound♪

18
00:01:23,660 --> 00:01:27,150
♪This love will never change♪

19
00:01:27,950 --> 00:01:35,080
♪We hold tight in this crazy era♪

20
00:01:35,160 --> 00:01:40,060
♪1990s love is what we rely on♪

21
00:01:40,100 --> 00:01:42,070
=Once More Love in 1995=

22
00:01:42,260 --> 00:01:44,925
=Episode 8=

23
00:01:45,150 --> 00:01:45,640
Boss.

24
00:01:45,862 --> 00:01:47,422
Ms. Zhuang is truly a genius.

25
00:01:47,460 --> 00:01:49,260
Thanks to Jinxin's
Journey to the West cards,

26
00:01:49,275 --> 00:01:50,756
our instant noodles

27
00:01:51,040 --> 00:01:53,400
are selling like hot cakes nationwide.

28
00:01:53,840 --> 00:01:56,519
In just two weeks, our market share

29
00:01:56,519 --> 00:01:58,439
has increased by 15.3%.

30
00:01:59,159 --> 00:02:00,319
What is she doing now?

31
00:02:01,150 --> 00:02:01,710
Huh?

32
00:02:02,925 --> 00:02:03,690
I meant Zhuang Yan.

33
00:02:05,075 --> 00:02:06,116
Ms. Zhuang?

34
00:02:06,487 --> 00:02:08,560
When I went to the mall today
to verify the data,

35
00:02:08,750 --> 00:02:09,551
I ran into her.

36
00:02:09,987 --> 00:02:10,946
She was

37
00:02:11,800 --> 00:02:12,439
buying gifts.

38
00:02:14,199 --> 00:02:15,159
Buying gifts?

39
00:02:16,425 --> 00:02:17,145
For who?

40
00:02:18,080 --> 00:02:19,479
I don't know.

41
00:02:21,199 --> 00:02:22,280
Could Ms. Zhuang

42
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:24,662
have a crush?

43
00:02:25,240 --> 00:02:26,680
She hasn't been here that long.

44
00:02:26,800 --> 00:02:28,159
She doesn't even know many people.

45
00:02:29,520 --> 00:02:31,075
Ms. Zhuang is beautiful.

46
00:02:31,439 --> 00:02:32,280
There must be

47
00:02:32,550 --> 00:02:33,719
plenty of people pursuing her.

48
00:02:34,337 --> 00:02:36,457
Seeing how carefully
she picked out the gift,

49
00:02:36,457 --> 00:02:37,775
it must be for her crush.

50
00:02:37,775 --> 00:02:39,090
Do you have nothing better to do?

51
00:02:39,100 --> 00:02:40,390
Why are you still standing here?

52
00:02:40,775 --> 00:02:41,296
I...

53
00:02:44,039 --> 00:02:44,759
Ah...

54
00:02:45,199 --> 00:02:45,960
Alright.

55
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:52,199
♪Today is a good day♪

56
00:02:52,560 --> 00:02:56,039
♪Everything you wish for comes true♪

57
00:02:57,280 --> 00:02:58,840
♪Mom♪

58
00:02:59,319 --> 00:03:02,080
♪Mom in the candlelight♪

59
00:03:04,439 --> 00:03:04,919
Ah.

60
00:03:06,175 --> 00:03:07,015
What are you doing?

61
00:03:07,650 --> 00:03:09,850
You've never been so hardworking
since you moved in.

62
00:03:10,599 --> 00:03:11,919
What's so special about today?

63
00:03:13,319 --> 00:03:15,240
Today is just an ordinary day,

64
00:03:15,462 --> 00:03:16,983
but tomorrow is a good day.

65
00:03:17,462 --> 00:03:18,742
Are you free tomorrow?

66
00:03:24,479 --> 00:03:25,680
Tomorrow?

67
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:27,560
Maybe.

68
00:03:28,280 --> 00:03:29,439
I guess so.

69
00:03:29,439 --> 00:03:30,730
I'll ask Li to check my schedule.

70
00:03:31,240 --> 00:03:32,280
Maybe?

71
00:03:32,479 --> 00:03:33,240
Ah!

72
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:42,759
Are you free tomorrow?

73
00:03:45,159 --> 00:03:46,199
Yes.

74
00:03:51,262 --> 00:03:54,225
♪Flipping to a photo from that year♪

75
00:03:54,225 --> 00:03:56,945
Thanks to your
quick reflexes and agility.

76
00:03:57,439 --> 00:03:58,400
Thanks.

77
00:04:00,039 --> 00:04:01,240
Then tomorrow...

78
00:04:02,840 --> 00:04:04,240
Wait for my call tomorrow.

79
00:04:04,240 --> 00:04:07,840
♪I run back along the dates♪

80
00:04:07,840 --> 00:04:09,199
(What's wrong with me?)

81
00:04:09,919 --> 00:04:12,479
(Why do I suddenly find
Qin Mo kind of cute?)

82
00:04:19,319 --> 00:04:21,720
Go ahead and do your thing.
I'm going to rest.

83
00:04:25,862 --> 00:04:29,862
♪Open an umbrella early
at the street corner♪

84
00:04:31,350 --> 00:04:35,550
♪So you won't get wet
when you turn around♪

85
00:04:37,837 --> 00:04:40,937
♪Dodging that icy storm♪

86
00:04:55,112 --> 00:04:55,873
Where's the gift?

87
00:04:57,399 --> 00:04:57,759
Huh?

88
00:04:57,920 --> 00:04:59,137
I've got everything ready.

89
00:04:59,237 --> 00:05:00,500
You haven't prepared yours yet?

90
00:05:00,680 --> 00:05:01,560
So direct?

91
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:03,137
Asking for a gift right away?

92
00:05:03,237 --> 00:05:04,558
What's wrong with being direct?

93
00:05:05,337 --> 00:05:08,319
If you want to express your feelings,
you should go all in on the ceremony

94
00:05:08,319 --> 00:05:09,639
and confess outright.

95
00:05:10,362 --> 00:05:12,040
This kind of approach

96
00:05:12,040 --> 00:05:13,199
goes straight to the point.

97
00:05:13,639 --> 00:05:15,079
It's called a direct shot.

98
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:17,087
A direct shot?

99
00:05:17,720 --> 00:05:19,199
It's indeed a bit above your level.

100
00:05:20,500 --> 00:05:21,690
Forget it. It's not important.

101
00:05:22,625 --> 00:05:24,759
You did prepare a gift, right?

102
00:05:25,079 --> 00:05:26,839
Take it out.

103
00:05:32,275 --> 00:05:32,836
What's this?

104
00:05:39,120 --> 00:05:41,079
No way, man.

105
00:05:43,639 --> 00:05:45,600
You've known Shanshan for so long.

106
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:46,480
She finally came home,

107
00:05:46,500 --> 00:05:48,279
and all you give her
are two movie tickets?

108
00:05:48,279 --> 00:05:49,839
Why did you choose movie tickets?

109
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:54,439
You're not trying
to pursue Shanshan, are you?

110
00:05:55,160 --> 00:05:55,800
Me?

111
00:05:56,160 --> 00:05:57,120
Pursue Shanshan?

112
00:05:57,210 --> 00:05:58,319
What nonsense are you talking about?

113
00:05:58,319 --> 00:05:59,279
She's like my sister.

114
00:05:59,350 --> 00:06:00,550
There's no way I'll pursue her.

115
00:06:02,120 --> 00:06:02,600
Mo.

116
00:06:02,920 --> 00:06:03,800
Yan.

117
00:06:04,680 --> 00:06:05,399
I'm back.

118
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:08,825
Shanshan, I missed you so much.

119
00:06:08,879 --> 00:06:10,600
I missed you too.

120
00:06:12,639 --> 00:06:13,375
Welcome home.

121
00:06:14,319 --> 00:06:15,199
This is your gift.

122
00:06:15,519 --> 00:06:17,360
Thank you, Yan.

123
00:06:22,439 --> 00:06:23,120
Shanshan.

124
00:06:23,319 --> 00:06:24,680
It's a big day today.

125
00:06:24,800 --> 00:06:25,680
Welcome home.

126
00:06:26,287 --> 00:06:27,366
I've got two movie tickets.

127
00:06:27,487 --> 00:06:28,566
Go watch it with a friend.

128
00:06:28,959 --> 00:06:30,439
Thank you, Qin.

129
00:06:30,639 --> 00:06:33,075
But Zeyang already asked me
to watch this movie with him.

130
00:06:33,125 --> 00:06:34,360
We already have tickets.

131
00:06:36,560 --> 00:06:40,120
Perfect. Qin and I are watching it too.

132
00:06:40,279 --> 00:06:41,279
Let's watch together.

133
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:42,839
Yes.

134
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:44,600
Together.

135
00:06:45,279 --> 00:06:45,920
Sure.

136
00:06:56,319 --> 00:06:57,639
It's all your fault for delaying.

137
00:06:57,639 --> 00:06:58,560
We lost them, didn't we?

138
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:01,839
Who was it that fell asleep
during the movie?

139
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:03,560
Your drool even got on me.

140
00:07:03,959 --> 00:07:05,439
Why didn't you keep an eye on them?

141
00:07:05,600 --> 00:07:06,759
I came to watch a movie,

142
00:07:06,759 --> 00:07:08,000
not to tail people.

143
00:07:08,130 --> 00:07:09,680
If my mom got pregnant with me today...

144
00:07:10,560 --> 00:07:11,360
What?

145
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:14,399
Forget it. You wouldn't get it anyway.

146
00:07:15,037 --> 00:07:18,050
Bottom line, Zhou Zeyang
can't be alone with Shanshan.

147
00:07:22,600 --> 00:07:25,399
Even if you think
Zhou Zeyang doesn't like Shanshan,

148
00:07:25,920 --> 00:07:27,560
I think you should trust Shanshan.

149
00:07:27,560 --> 00:07:29,000
She can handle her own feelings

150
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:30,240
and knows what she wants.

151
00:07:30,240 --> 00:07:31,437
You can't control her forever.

152
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:31,879
You...

153
00:07:39,560 --> 00:07:42,160
Have you seen
a movie called Back to 1995?

154
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:43,800
Another movie?

155
00:07:45,279 --> 00:07:45,560
No.

156
00:07:46,720 --> 00:07:47,519
What's it about?

157
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:52,120
It's about a mother and daughter.

158
00:07:53,439 --> 00:07:55,120
The mother is kind and beautiful.

159
00:07:55,519 --> 00:07:57,600
She never hurt anyone,

160
00:07:57,687 --> 00:07:59,406
but she was abandoned by her family,

161
00:07:59,406 --> 00:08:00,447
betrayed by her friends,

162
00:08:00,500 --> 00:08:01,660
and deceived by her lover.

163
00:08:02,712 --> 00:08:04,120
They ganged up together

164
00:08:04,120 --> 00:08:05,639
and ruined her entire family.

165
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:08,920
(Late Mother, Zhuang Shanshan)
She left this world with regrets.

166
00:08:09,712 --> 00:08:11,272
Her useless daughter

167
00:08:11,439 --> 00:08:13,680
could do nothing but cry.

168
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:16,600
But one day,

169
00:08:16,762 --> 00:08:17,923
a miracle happened.

170
00:08:19,412 --> 00:08:21,439
The daughter returned
to before her mother died.

171
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:24,959
All the misfortune had not occurred.

172
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:26,240
She swore

173
00:08:26,240 --> 00:08:29,040
to eliminate every danger and villain
around her mother,

174
00:08:29,160 --> 00:08:31,439
reversing her tragic life at its root.

175
00:08:32,720 --> 00:08:34,159
What's the ending of the movie?

176
00:08:35,375 --> 00:08:36,895
I haven't seen the ending,

177
00:08:39,087 --> 00:08:40,648
but I hope she succeeds.

178
00:08:41,759 --> 00:08:43,399
If she did succeed,

179
00:08:44,462 --> 00:08:46,343
the mother
wouldn't have her daughter anymore.

180
00:08:47,759 --> 00:08:49,440
But for the daughter,

181
00:08:49,919 --> 00:08:53,039
having her mother live again
matters most.

182
00:09:04,519 --> 00:09:06,159
After the new cup noodles launched,

183
00:09:06,159 --> 00:09:07,520
market feedback has been positive.

184
00:09:07,562 --> 00:09:09,442
Our sales have also been rising steadily.

185
00:09:10,039 --> 00:09:11,080
Market share

186
00:09:11,080 --> 00:09:12,159
has increased from 9%

187
00:09:12,159 --> 00:09:13,799
to 20%.

188
00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:18,759
That's all?

189
00:09:20,600 --> 00:09:21,440
Boss.

190
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:23,159
Are you alright?

191
00:09:24,639 --> 00:09:25,240
Li.

192
00:09:25,720 --> 00:09:26,799
Let me ask you something.

193
00:09:27,610 --> 00:09:29,093
Have you ever felt sorry for someone?

194
00:09:31,480 --> 00:09:32,080
Felt sorry?

195
00:09:32,279 --> 00:09:33,000
I mean,

196
00:09:33,399 --> 00:09:34,840
someone you're not that close to

197
00:09:34,840 --> 00:09:36,039
or even don't get along with.

198
00:09:36,575 --> 00:09:38,559
But when you see her being wronged,

199
00:09:39,037 --> 00:09:40,956
you somehow feel bad for her.

200
00:09:42,787 --> 00:09:44,039
Have you experienced that?

201
00:09:44,279 --> 00:09:45,360
Ah.

202
00:09:45,900 --> 00:09:46,579
Boss.

203
00:09:46,975 --> 00:09:48,975
You've fallen for Ms. Zhuang.

204
00:09:52,039 --> 00:09:53,039
When did I mention her?

205
00:09:57,200 --> 00:09:58,759
You never said her name,

206
00:09:59,159 --> 00:10:00,639
yet every word was about her.

207
00:10:01,320 --> 00:10:03,240
Ever since Ms. Zhuang arrived,

208
00:10:03,437 --> 00:10:06,277
your emotions
have become more and more unstable.

209
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:08,320
You find her annoying,

210
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:09,559
yet keeps indulging her.

211
00:10:10,200 --> 00:10:13,039
When she gets wronged,
you can't help but feel sorry for her.

212
00:10:13,275 --> 00:10:14,594
If that's not love,

213
00:10:15,360 --> 00:10:16,080
then what is?

214
00:10:18,440 --> 00:10:19,879
I shouldn't have talked to you.

215
00:10:20,262 --> 00:10:20,823
Get out.

216
00:10:32,799 --> 00:10:33,799
What's wrong, Shanshan?

217
00:10:34,559 --> 00:10:36,399
I think I saw Yan.

218
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:38,480
That's impossible.

219
00:10:38,960 --> 00:10:40,200
It really looked like her.

220
00:10:40,200 --> 00:10:41,000
I'll go check.

221
00:10:41,840 --> 00:10:42,320
Shanshan.

222
00:10:43,080 --> 00:10:44,375
You must've imagined it.

223
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:45,660
Think about it.

224
00:10:46,159 --> 00:10:47,520
If Yan were really here,

225
00:10:47,530 --> 00:10:49,039
wouldn't she jump out to break us up?

226
00:10:49,039 --> 00:10:50,678
You're going back
to the troupe tomorrow.

227
00:10:50,780 --> 00:10:51,937
Let's enjoy our date tonight.

228
00:10:52,037 --> 00:10:52,676
Alright?

229
00:10:54,440 --> 00:10:55,080
Sure.

230
00:10:55,362 --> 00:10:56,122
Let's go.

231
00:11:02,600 --> 00:11:03,960
This place...

232
00:11:14,525 --> 00:11:17,126
Zhang Guolong, kidnapping is illegal.

233
00:11:18,039 --> 00:11:18,919
Did anyone

234
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:21,039
see me kidnapping you?

235
00:11:22,519 --> 00:11:23,519
Ms. Zhuang.

236
00:11:23,799 --> 00:11:25,360
Don't you think we should talk this out?

237
00:11:26,519 --> 00:11:28,399
Mr. Zhang, say what you want quickly.

238
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:30,440
I still have company business.

239
00:11:31,159 --> 00:11:32,159
If Qin Mo can't find me,

240
00:11:32,325 --> 00:11:33,325
he'll go crazy.

241
00:11:36,799 --> 00:11:38,950
You're threatening me with Qin Mo?

242
00:11:39,050 --> 00:11:39,679
Miss.

243
00:11:40,480 --> 00:11:42,399
I'm kidnapping you right now.

244
00:11:42,675 --> 00:11:43,996
You think I'm playing games?

245
00:11:44,387 --> 00:11:46,159
You're staring death in the face.

246
00:11:46,440 --> 00:11:47,679
To be honest,

247
00:11:48,320 --> 00:11:50,200
I know I'll live until 2025.

248
00:11:53,240 --> 00:11:55,840
You're really stubborn.

249
00:11:55,840 --> 00:11:57,180
You're not afraid of dying at all.

250
00:11:57,720 --> 00:11:59,559
I thought you wanted to destroy Qin Mo.

251
00:12:00,440 --> 00:12:02,200
Turns out you want me dead.

252
00:12:02,559 --> 00:12:03,600
I swear,

253
00:12:04,240 --> 00:12:06,039
dealing with Qin Mo was sincere.

254
00:12:06,200 --> 00:12:07,919
Nonsense.

255
00:12:08,159 --> 00:12:09,679
My reputation is ruined.

256
00:12:09,679 --> 00:12:10,879
The entire warehouse of goods is trash.

257
00:12:10,879 --> 00:12:11,799
Nothing can be sold.

258
00:12:11,799 --> 00:12:12,720
What do I do?

259
00:12:13,159 --> 00:12:15,240
You're the first person
who dared screw me over.

260
00:12:16,559 --> 00:12:18,759
So tell me how I should repay you.

261
00:12:20,062 --> 00:12:20,862
Mr. Zhang.

262
00:12:22,440 --> 00:12:25,200
Instant Noodle Buddies
already put you ahead of Qin Mo,

263
00:12:25,519 --> 00:12:27,600
but you still
want to use the packaging issue

264
00:12:27,600 --> 00:12:28,639
to bring down Jinxin.

265
00:12:28,919 --> 00:12:29,840
I can't agree to that.

266
00:12:30,412 --> 00:12:32,013
If you keep targeting Jinxin,

267
00:12:32,320 --> 00:12:33,960
get ready for bankruptcy declaration.

268
00:12:34,937 --> 00:12:35,736
No, you...

269
00:12:36,519 --> 00:12:38,080
You're threatening me?

270
00:12:40,480 --> 00:12:42,759
How dare you threaten me?

271
00:12:44,320 --> 00:12:45,679
I'm not threatening you.

272
00:12:51,240 --> 00:12:54,000
Instead of playing gangster here,
why not trade me for something real?

273
00:12:59,360 --> 00:13:02,240
I don't believe a word you say.

274
00:13:02,960 --> 00:13:03,840
Qin Mo values me.

275
00:13:04,879 --> 00:13:07,559
Otherwise, how would
someone of unknown background like me

276
00:13:07,559 --> 00:13:09,500
be thriving at Jinxin?

277
00:13:09,562 --> 00:13:11,159
You have two choices.

278
00:13:11,775 --> 00:13:14,125
First, trading me
for what you want from Qin Mo.

279
00:13:16,320 --> 00:13:18,320
Second, waiting for Qin Mo
to deal with your body.

280
00:13:19,537 --> 00:13:20,616
Take your pick.

281
00:13:29,360 --> 00:13:31,360
I just want to see

282
00:13:32,120 --> 00:13:34,039
how important you are to Qin Mo.

283
00:14:05,287 --> 00:14:08,925
♪The old dial tone circles in my ear♪

284
00:14:09,050 --> 00:14:12,362
♪Faded tickets point to a cicada summer♪

285
00:14:12,525 --> 00:14:16,112
♪The videotape
whispers your image in the frame♪

286
00:14:16,412 --> 00:14:19,700
♪Against the light, the plaid shirt
reveals a clear and transparent smile♪

287
00:14:19,925 --> 00:14:23,550
♪I'm a clumsy guest in a frozen scene♪

288
00:14:23,712 --> 00:14:27,050
♪How do I answer familiar lines?♪

289
00:14:27,125 --> 00:14:30,837
♪I know
the train will leave this station♪

290
00:14:30,887 --> 00:14:34,750
♪I know the ending's in a faded future♪

291
00:14:34,812 --> 00:14:40,862
♪Yet I want to approach that warmth♪

292
00:14:42,037 --> 00:14:48,775
♪Even one second rewrites missed lines♪

293
00:14:49,062 --> 00:14:53,337
♪Rewind to 1995,
back to the street we met♪

294
00:14:53,337 --> 00:14:56,637
♪Wind blows through the sycamore leaves
and lands on your shoulder♪

295
00:14:56,712 --> 00:15:01,012
♪I wish I could pause and stop time♪

296
00:15:01,075 --> 00:15:04,725
♪Let unspoken love
be preserved forever as amber♪

297
00:15:04,725 --> 00:15:08,287
♪Rewind to 1995,
gentle touch of fingertips♪

298
00:15:08,337 --> 00:15:11,600
♪Star sparks in your eyes burn my chest♪

299
00:15:11,600 --> 00:15:15,350
♪This looping script
is beyond my saving♪

300
00:15:15,350 --> 00:15:22,062
♪I can only stay with you till the end
in this inverted hourglass♪
